payload.sql:
SELECT "messages".* FROM "messages"  WHERE ((sent_messageable_type = 'User' and
                                                  sent_messageable_id = 1 and
                                                  sender_delete = 'f' and sender_permanent_delete = 'f') or
                                                  (received_messageable_type = 'User' and
                                                  received_messageable_id = 1 and
                                                  recipient_delete = 'f' and recipient_permanent_delete = 'f')) ORDER BY created_at desc
payload.name: ActsAsMessageable::Message Load
